{"tid":698813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：霸𨋢搬屋工踢傷女保安","createTime":"2018-06-12T04:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T05:10:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1e68b437c24890475e60fdac23bd89638b61099c","tid":698813,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180612/20418256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F20418256&d=2lwlGKa7mSP44RAh4nKyUp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=60b468b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F20418256&h=8f5b00e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180612/20418256</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月12日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：霸𨋢搬屋工踢傷女保安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180612/large/a12a04a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180612%2Flarge%2Fa12a04a.gif&h=08a2aef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■紅褲搬運工人起飛腳踢向女保安。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搬屋搵着啲唔專業嘅公司同工人，有時真係累街坊。前日（10號）下晝12點左右，鰂魚涌康景花園B座有住客搬屋，兩個搬運工人霸住部𨋢搬嘢上樓，其中一個着黑衫嘅工人喺𨋢入面接應，另一個40幾歲着灰色衫紅褲嘅工人就喺𨋢外面。佢哋將好多袋嘢放喺𨋢門外阻住晒，仲搞到居民無𨋢用，居民梗係投訴啦。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180612/large/a12a04b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180612%2Flarge%2Fa12a04b.gif&h=862da915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉事公司：唔知邊個<br />\n<br />\n22歲姓鄭女保安員嚟到處理，當時着紅褲嗰位工人推完一板車嘢入𨋢塞滿咗，仲想推另一板車入𨋢，女保安見到咁，於是就企喺𨋢入面，阻止工人再搬貨入𨋢。點知呢個紅褲搬運工人竟然發爛渣，起飛腳踢傷呢位弱質纖纖嘅女保安。<br />\n<br />\n事後警員接到呢位女保安報案，趕到現場調查，將女保安送去東區醫院治理，但個涉案工人就已經走咗。案件列作襲擊，暫時無人被捕。有目擊事發經過嘅居民，睇唔過眼個搬運工踢傷女保安，就向《蘋果》爆相爆片，一定要追緝兇徒咁話！<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》打去問過涉事嘅實惠搬屋有限公司，對方有個自稱姓黎嘅男人就一味話唔清楚件事，又話唔知邊個工人踢傷女保安喎。不過閉路電視就清楚影到工人個樣囉。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：三隻醉貓擒的士踢又踩<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點‧即聽"},{"pid":"d8e284ea6144658ae244cf9b326c33c2b21fa223","tid":698813,"uid":28619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:43:59.000Z","msg":"22歲女保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07dbb87bac2aa59aa9899bfd033f3e359764126c","tid":698813,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:48:12.000Z","msg":"為份工傷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要蝦妹妹仔，不能原諒"},{"pid":"25dc9c5a57f2d3c75758764bc9372d8665ce6917","tid":698813,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"紅褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9b9bbd596c4eb5bc7bd6581363520212cac0d9","tid":698813,"uid":71433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"入去坐啦"},{"pid":"3afe1ab6f3d64c43ffef97bd1a00b12dc1a9d943","tid":698813,"uid":105888,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"裝修佬同地盤佬真係同蝻冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907b210a510a85ddf7e0dc55e839b36547746570","tid":698813,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8e284ea6144658ae244cf9b326c33c2b21fa223","tid":698813,"uid":28619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:43:59.000Z","msg":"22歲女保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"估唔到你好呢味"},{"pid":"203717b78d74dd87d4477b2fda55fe227df1daae","tid":698813,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"907b210a510a85ddf7e0dc55e839b36547746570","tid":698813,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8e284ea6144658ae244cf9b326c33c2b21fa223","tid":698813,"uid":28619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:43:59.000Z","msg":"22歲女保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"估唔到你好呢味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"22歲女仔係靚女都叫佢做物管啦<br />\n使出黎做保安？"},{"pid":"a5ad0f21c02c4085b5add4f348eb0d8e85863204","tid":698813,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"明知佢地霸住部lift阻到人,仲阻住佢地入貨,搬多一轉阻得咪仲耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbc05695597ef4ed2bd556fe62236ec36f97603","tid":698813,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"22歲做保安，係咪新移民黎架"},{"pid":"2a2c688507b607bffb96d8849410766b2df052df","tid":698813,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ee56b698c5054c7830624bb0a60544df0945d4","tid":698813,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"為左幫人搬屋呢d工而犯法<br />\n真係唔明佢個腦諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}